Package com.innerspec.main

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataFrame
    Displays a table of layer names, thicknesses, and file names.
    DataFrameModel
    A table model that handles the data population of the table in DataFrame.
    DoubleTableEditor
    Implements a cell editor that uses a formatted text field to edit Double values.
    GerberFile
    A data type containing information about each Gerber file.
    GerberFileManager
    Handles the creation and writing of Gerber file data.
    Layer
    A data type containing all the information related to each layer.
    LayerManager
    LayerManager contains methods to populate and return the layers array.
    PrimaryFileSelectorFrame
    Displays a file select screen with which the user can select the dxf file to convert.
    ProgressFrame
    Displays information related to the end output of the Gerber file.
    SplashScreenManager
    Manages the display of text to the splash screen.
    ThicknessManager
    Contains the main methods for handling thicknesses for files.
